        {
            "_id": "lVPiJuTH9q1Leaik",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Humiliate the Fish",
            "sort": 800000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> A creature is hooked by Arth's fish hook and adjacent to Arth</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> Arth yanks the hook free, causing @Damage[4d8[slashing]] damage to the creature (@Check[fortitude|dc:28|basic|options:inflicts:prone] save), who also falls @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Prone] if they fail that Fortitude save.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": []
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "sq0VrKKaIL5bX85J",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Reel In",
            "sort": 900000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Arth pulls the rope attached to his hook. If he has no creature hooked, the fish hook returns to his hand. If a creature is hooked, Arth attempts an @Check[athletics|against:fortitude|options:forced-movement] check against the creature's Fortitude DC, pulling it up to 30 feet closer on a success (60 feet on a critical success).</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": [
                        "manipulate"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "cwIqYYLTEgIfpZKa",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Swear",
            "sort": 1000000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Arth unleashes a string of invectives. Each creature that hears him must attempt a @Check[will|dc:28|traits:concentrate,curse,manipulate] save, with the effects of @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Mariner's Curse], and is then temporarily immune for 24 hours. Even on a failed save, the curse ends automatically after 24 hours.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
